org.uclab.mm.icl.hlc.ContextOntologyManager

Class ContextQueryGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.uclab.mm.icl.hlc.ContextOntologyManager.ContextQueryGenerator

  • public class ContextQueryGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Context Query Generator: Subcomponent of the Context Ontology Manager which generates the SPARQL queries required by the Context Handler to find the matching Context instances stored in the Context Ontology Storage.
    Since:
    2015-10-28
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Claudia Villalonga
